  "title": "Field resistance in extra-short-duration pigeonpea lines to dry root rot",
  "abstract": "The mortality of 30 genotypes of pigeon pea caused by Rhizoctonia bataticola (Macrophomina phaseolina) was investigated with and without irrigation, in alfisols and vertisols, in Andhra Pradesh, India, in 1988/89 and 1992/93. Some lines showed a promising degree of resistance",
